6bc7053381460d39a","tid":2451953,"uid":266342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"講真將去踢上大陸就最啱㗎喇<br />\n本身佢已經係一個大陸人（深圳出世）<br />\n一係大陸你自己判佢死刑<br />\n反正你覺得全宇宙都係你嘅一部份㗎啦<br />\n更何況大陸同台灣其實有司法互助<br />\n咁咪經大陸隻手送去台灣囉<br />\n<br />\n根本就好易解決係唔做咋嘛"},{"pid":"458fe135a31c3c50384ddbf04fc316056c2912c0","tid":2451953,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"憑我本事走甩點解要返去？<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46c6618fb39998e647d590f7be3aab66e6d682e","tid":2451953,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74fb81ad3e60c2d7fc68c43ada7109af195ceab","tid":2451953,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"佳仔唔願意走<br />\n無人有權捉佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"柒婆: 證明香港有人權，好自由"}]}